## Summary
This documentation explains the User Composition Chart in Amplitude, which displays the breakdown of active users based on a single user property, showing how to set up this analysis by selecting user properties and segments rather than events, and how to interpret the results using "Latest Value," "All Values," or "Cross Property Values" measurement options.

